                     <interp inst="t16940524-29-off113" type="offenceSubcategory" value="forgery"></interp>
               Common Defrauder and Cheater of Their Majesties Subjects of their monies, which he did by Forging and Counterfeiting Letters signed with the Sign of the Post-Office General; particularly, he delivered two Letters to one Mr. 
                     <persName id="t16940524-29-victim98" type="victimName">
                        Robert 
                        Tempest
                     <interp inst="t16940524-29-victim98" type="surname" value="Tempest"></interp>
